                "invention-title": [
                    "Low-carbon thick material layer sintering method based on comprehensive injection and sintering machine",
                    "一种基于综合喷吹的低碳厚料层烧结方法及烧结机"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a low-carbon thick material layer sintering method based on comprehensive injection and a sintering machine. The sintering method comprises the steps that thick material layer sintering is carried out in the mode of two-time material distribution and two-time ignition; carrying out first-time injection on the sintered material surface after the first-time ignition, and carrying out second-time injection on the sintered material surface after the second-time ignition; mixed gas of fuel gas and steam is used for injection; according to the highest temperature of the sintering material layer and the proportion of the biomass carbon powder in the sintering fuel, the first-time injection total heat, the second-time injection total heat and the corresponding supply heat proportion of the fuel gas and the steam are determined; the problem that non-fossil biomass fuel cannot be applied to sintering production in a large proportion is solved; and the problem that the actual injection effect is affected due to the fact that key technical parameters such as the gas fuel supplementing amount, the mixing proportion and the injection position are difficult to control in ultra-thick material layer sintering hydrogen-rich gas and steam mixed injection is solved, and high-quality and low-emission sintering production is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种基于综合喷吹的低碳厚料层烧结方法及烧结机，所述烧结方法包括：采用两次布料、两次点火的方式进行厚料层烧结；在第一次点火后的烧结料面上进行第一次喷吹，在第二次点火后的烧结料面上进行第二次喷吹；所述喷吹使用燃气与蒸汽的混合气；依据烧结料层最高温度及烧结燃料中生物质炭粉的占比确定第一次喷吹总热量、第二次喷吹总热量及相应的所述燃气与所述蒸汽的供应热量比例；解决非化石生物质燃料无法大比例应用于烧结生产的问题；及解决超厚料层烧结富氢燃气和蒸汽混合喷吹，气体燃料补入量、混配比例和喷吹位置等关键技术参数难以把控，影响实际喷吹效果的问题，实现高质量、低排放烧结生产。"
                }
            ]
